MAIN.translated: 我在家里好寂寞啊，快过来。顺便，记得走员工通道。 T xx

MAIN.original: Where were you? I kept my boyf out the house forever thinking you were coming. Thanks a lot. T
MAIN.translated: 你人呢？我以为你会来，一直不让男友回来。多谢啊。 T

MAIN.original: Opps! Boyf found out about you. Mommy's a bad girl. No more treats if she keeps doing you. Sorry. T xx
MAIN.translated: 糟了！男友发现你的事了，娘子是个坏姑娘。再跟你做她就要分手了。 T xx

MAIN.original: Sneak peak of what u'll b getting if u come round right now! Vik xx
MAIN.translated: 图透一下，现在过来你你就能得到啦！ Vik xx

MAIN.original: u must b tired running threw my head all day. :) come round. Vik xx
MAIN.translated: 你在我的脑海里跑了一天，一定很累吧。 :) 来找我。 Vik xx

MAIN.original: Get here now stud. Been thinkin about u! Need those hands on me! Vik xx
MAIN.translated: 快过来，风流小子。我一直在想你！需要你温暖的大手抚摸！ Vik xx

MAIN.original: thought u were coming over. Poo! Poo! Poo! Soon pls! Vik xx
MAIN.translated: 我还以为你会来。大错特错了！拜托来一次吧！ Vik xx

MAIN.original: umm... Hard 2 do, but things not working out... Need to call us off. Soz! Vik xxx
MAIN.translated: 呃...很难受，但不可能继续了...只能这样散了。抱歉！ Vik xxx

MAIN.original: Te gusta? Come around now, my matador! Besos
MAIN.translated: 中意吗？快来吧，我的斗牛士！ 亲亲

MAIN.original: Mamma wants to gobble down your little croqueta. Come to me. Besos
MAIN.translated: 老娘想要吞下你的小可乐饼。来找我。 亲亲

MAIN.original: My day has been so bland. I need some spice to give it excitement. Please come around. Besos
MAIN.translated: 我的生活如此乏味，需要一些香辛料才能得到色彩。你快来吧。 亲亲

MAIN.original: My bed stayed cold. You do not need to apologize. The matador is meant to have many mistresses. Just do not forget our heat together. Besos.
MAIN.translated: 我的床还是那么冰冷。你没必要道歉的，斗牛士确实会有很多女主人。只是别忘了我们在一起时的干柴烈火。 亲亲

MAIN.original: Matador, our brief, turbulent affair is over. I wish you heat and love on the rest of your journey. Besos
MAIN.translated: 斗牛士，长话短说吧，儿女情长该结束了。希望你在接下来的旅途中也会遇到热情的爱。

MAIN.original: Hey look - no airbrushing. Come around 2 mine for the full catwalk show. ;)
MAIN.translated: 嘿，快看，无修的图。快来我家看完整的时装秀。 ;)

MAIN.original: Hey Dude, I need a work out. Come by and give me 1. ;)
MAIN.translated: 嘿，老兄，我想跟你来一发。快来满足我吧。 ;)

MAIN.original: I just got waxed like a baby for this shoot. Stop by and enjoy it. :-o
MAIN.translated: 为了拍这张照，我特意做了个蜜蜡脱毛。快来享用吧。 :-o

MAIN.original: ummm. :-/ where were you? Time is $, motherfucker!! :(
MAIN.translated: 呃... :-/ 你去哪了？时间就是$，混蛋！！ :(

MAIN.original: Sorry, dude. Upgrading 2 a better model. Don't get 2 :(
MAIN.translated: 抱歉，老兄，我要成为更好的模特。别太 :(

MAIN.original: Hey Sugar, I've got a craving for somehting sweet. U free? xx
MAIN.translated: 嘿，甜心，我现在很渴望快感。你有空吗？ xx

MAIN.original: A girl gets kind of lonely in this city. If only someone would come around and keep her entertained...
MAIN.translated: 在这座城市，我一个女孩子还是有点寂寞。真希望能有人给我带来乐趣啊...

MAIN.original: What's a girl got to do to get some action in this town?! I'll be at my apartment for a bit if you wanna come by.xx
MAIN.translated: 女孩子要怎么做，才能在自由城得到鱼水之欢？！我现在在公寓里，你想来就来吧。 xx

MAIN.original: I guess something came up, Sugar. I got to get used to people in LC not calling to cancel. I'll learn one day!
MAIN.translated: 你一定是有急事吧，甜心。我会慢慢适应自由城不说一声就不来的习俗的。我会适应这里的！

MAIN.original: Hey Sugar, hate to do this by txt, but seems like the LC way. Stuff ain't working out. Take care. xx
MAIN.translated: 嘿，甜心，我也不想发短信说这种事，但这似乎是自由城的作派。我们不可能了，保重。 xx

MAIN.original: Oi! Get ur arse around here and sort me out! I'm gagging for it!
MAIN.translated: 喂！快他妈过来满足我！我要忍不住了！

MAIN.original: Woteva, stop being a nonce and come round here! I'm gagging.
MAIN.translated: 算了，别那么混蛋，过来找我！我忍不住了！

MAIN.original: Are you going to be a poof or are you coming round here to smash my back doors down. I'm waiting!
MAIN.translated: 你是要做一个娘炮，还是过来轰入我的后门？我等着你！

MAIN.original: Oi, you vain twat. Where the fuck were you? Wotevz, bruv.
MAIN.translated: 喂，你这个自大狂，你他妈人呢？算了，兄弟。

MAIN.original: Listen bruv, can't keep doing this. I'm an independent woman, innit. Latz.
MAIN.translated: 听着，兄弟，不能再这样了。我是独立女性，懂吧。再见。

MAIN.original: I'm bored enough to take photos of myself. Want to find out what else I'm bored enough to do?
MAIN.translated: 我已经玩自拍玩腻了。想知道还有什么是我玩腻了的吗？

MAIN.original: Right. I'm bored. Get round here.
Not here for much longer. Want to remind me why I love soming bak to Liberty City?
MAIN.translated: 你好久没来了。可以来让我想起我爱来自由城的原因吗？

MAIN.original: Really not here for long enough to get messed round like this. Please don't stand me up again.
MAIN.translated: 好久没有一起做过了。别再放我鸽子了。

MAIN.original: I'm off! Give me a shout if you're ever over my way. Big kiss.
MAIN.translated: 我不玩了！你要是对我有过感情，就跟我说一声。爱你。

MAIN.original: Hey papi. Where u at? This shit's waiting for you!
MAIN.translated: 嘿，汉子。你在哪儿呢？我现在正等着你！

MAIN.original: Diga me, papi? Where u be? I need ur ass!
MAIN.translated: 告诉我，汉子，你在哪里？我需要你！

MAIN.original: Oh papi! Papi! I'm getting muy caliente just thinking 'bout you. Get here pronto!
MAIN.translated: 噢，汉子！汉子！光是想到你就让我浑身燥热。快过来啊！

MAIN.original: You turn stupid all of a sudden, papi? Where the fuck was u?
MAIN.translated: 你是一下子变傻了吗，汉子？你他妈去哪了？

MAIN.original: Yo, papi. I'm done with your ass. You gonna have to stick that thing of yours somewhere else. Sorry.
MAIN.translated: 哟，汉子，我和你结束了。你还是换个地方插你那玩意吧。抱歉。

MAIN.original: Time for the second act, sweetheart. Come on down.
MAIN.translated: 该上演第二幕了，甜心。快来吧。

MAIN.original: I've got a feeling I'm about to give my best performance. Get here.
MAIN.translated: 我现在的状态很好，可以带来最好的表现。速来。

MAIN.original: Call time, baby. Come around and impress me!
MAIN.translated: 到点了，宝贝。快来满足我吧！

MAIN.original: Think we must have got some crossed wires, I thought we were meant to meet up? Ummmm....
MAIN.translated: 我们是不是误会了什么，好像说好了要见面的吧？呃...

MAIN.original: Please don't call me again. Could get awkward. Later on, loser.
MAIN.translated: 请不要再联系我了，会很尴尬的。再见，失败者。

MAIN.original: Come by soon, darling. I've got something to show you that isn't in the pic... H xx
MAIN.translated: 快来啊，亲爱的。我要给你看看照片里没拍到的东西... H xx

MAIN.original: Come on over, darling. Just bought a new toy. H xx
MAIN.translated: 快来啊，亲爱的。我刚买了个新玩具。 H xx

MAIN.original: Come by, babes. Feeling toned post yoga, and need you to unwind me. H xx
MAIN.translated: 快来，宝贝。做完瑜伽感觉有点累，需要你来帮我放松。 H xx

MAIN.original: Hold up, babes. Think you got the power balance confused just now I'm the one who's meant to stand you up. Don't do it again. H xx
MAIN.translated: 等一下，宝贝，你好像搞错了我俩的关系，我才是有权放鸽子的人。别再鸽我了。 H xx

MAIN.original: Moving on, moving up, love. Don't forget me. Toodles! H xx
MAIN.translated: 向前进，向上走，亲爱的。勿忘我。拜拜啦！ H xx

MAIN.original: Me want snuggles. Come see me soon. xoxo
MAIN.translated: 我想要你的怀抱，快来找我。么么

MAIN.original: Smooches and snugs soon pls. Waiting now... xoxo
MAIN.translated: 要亲亲，要抱抱。我等着你...么么

MAIN.original: baby needs her blankee. Me suck suck all night long. You know where to come. xoxo
MAIN.translated: 宝宝需要她的毯子，我一整晚都要吸吸。你知道我在哪儿的。么么

MAIN.original: Didn't get those snuggles you promised! Made me really sad. xoxo
MAIN.translated: 没有得到说好的抱抱！宝宝哭哭。么么

MAIN.original: I don't think you're taking this seriously enough. Please don't call again. Been through this before sadly. xoxoxoxox
MAIN.translated: 我觉得你对这份感情不够认真，别再联系我了。之前就经历过这种事了。么么么么

MAIN.original: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!
MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

MAIN.original: ~s~Tony is not here during the day. Go to his apartment.
~s~Tony is not here during the day. Try again between 7pm and 7am.
MAIN.translated: ~s~Tony白天不在这儿。晚七点到早七点间再来吧。

MAIN.original: ~s~Tony is not at home at night. He is working in the clubs.
~s~Tony is not at home at night. Try again between 7am and 7pm.
MAIN.translated: ~s~Tony晚上不在家。早七点到晚七点间再来吧。

MAIN.original: ~s~Come back when you're not on a mission.
~s~Another fight will be on soon, come back in a while.
MAIN.translated: ~s~下场比赛还在准备，过会儿再来吧。

MAIN.original: Who do you want to play golf with?~n~Press ~PAD_A~ to play Armando.~n~Press ~PAD_B~ to play Henrique.~n~Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to exit.
MAIN.translated: 你想和谁打高尔夫？~n~按~PAD_A~和Armando打。~n~按~PAD_B~和Henrique打。~n~按~INPUT_PICKUP~退出。

MAIN.original: Who do you want to play golf with?~n~Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_MINIGAME_1~ to play Armando.~n~Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_MINIGAME_2~ to play Henrique.~n~Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to exit.
MAIN.translated: 你想和谁打高尔夫？~n~按~INPUT_FRONTEND_MINIGAME_1~和Armando打。~n~按~INPUT_FRONTEND_MINIGAME_2~和Henrique打。~n~按~INPUT_PICKUP~退出。

MAIN.original: The driving range is temporarily closed.
Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to move in the air. ~n~Press ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to activate parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~在空中移动。~n~按~INPUT_SPRINT~打开降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to move in the air. ~n~Press ~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~ to activate parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~在空中移动。~n~按~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~打开降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to shift body weight. ~n~Use ~PAD_LT~ and ~PAD_RT~ to apply left and right air brakes. ~n~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to detach the parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~控制身体重心。~n~按~PAD_LT~或~PAD_RT~进行急转。~n~按~INPUT_ENTER~抛弃降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to shift body weight. ~n~Use ~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~ and ~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~ to apply left and right air brakes. ~n~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to detach the parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~控制身体重心。~n~按~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~或~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~进行急转。~n~按~INPUT_ENTER~抛弃降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to shift body weight. ~n~Use ~PAD_LB~ and ~PAD_RB~ to apply left and right air brakes. ~n~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to detach the parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~控制身体重心。~n~按~PAD_LB~或~PAD_RB~进行急转。~n~按~INPUT_ENTER~脱离降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to shift body weight. ~n~Use ~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~ and ~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~ to apply left and right air brakes. ~n~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to detach the parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~ to view different cameras.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~控制身体重心。~n~按~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~或~INPUT_MOUSE_RMB~进行急转。~n~按~INPUT_ENTER~脱离降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~查看不同视角。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_ATTACK~ to put on the parachute.
Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to jump from this building.
Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to be airlifted for a base jump.
Move ~INPUT_LOOK_UP~ up and down to shake the bottle. Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to pop the cork. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to quit at any time.
MAIN.translated: 上下移动~INPUT_LOOK_UP~晃动酒瓶。按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~开瓶。按~INPUT_PICKUP~可随时退出。

MAIN.original: Move ~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~ up and down to shake the bottle. Press ~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~ to pop the cork. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to quit at any time.
MAIN.translated: 上下移动~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~晃动酒瓶。按~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~开瓶。按~INPUT_PICKUP~可随时退出。

MAIN.original: Rotate ~PAD_RSTICK_ROTATE~ at a steady speed to take a drink. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to quit.
Rotate ~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~ at a steady speed to take a drink. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to quit.
~s~Move ~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~ left or right to spray the champagne.
Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to drink a shot. Drinks are on the house.
Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to start a champagne drink off.
Go to the ~BLIP_106~ icon to take part in different base jumping activites.
MAIN.translated: 前往~BLIP_106~图标可以进行低空跳伞。

MAIN.original: Go to the ~BLIP_120~ icon to take part in L.C. Cage Fighters and become Liberty City's top brawler.
MAIN.translated: 前往~BLIP_120~图标参加自由城铁笼格斗，成为自由城拳王。

MAIN.original: Go to the ~BLIP_108~ icon to help out Armando and Henrique in drug wars.
MAIN.translated: 前往~BLIP_108~图标协助Armando和Henrique的毒品战争。

MAIN.original: Go to the ~BLIP_65~ icon to take part in multiple vehicle races.
MAIN.translated: 前往~BLIP_65~图标参加铁人三项。

MAIN.original: The main story has now been completed. You can repeat missions via the phone. Go to 'missions' then choose the mission you want to repeat. You can repeat missions as many times as you wish.
MAIN.translated: 主线剧情已完成，你可以通过手机重玩之前的任务。在「任务」中进行选择，就可以无限制地重玩所有任务。

MAIN.original: Go to the ~BLIP_121~ icon in Maisonette 9 during its opening times of 9pm-5am to partake in the club management job.
MAIN.translated: 晚上九点到早上五点之间，你可以前往9号豪宅的~BLIP_121~图标参与夜店经营。

MAIN.original: Yusuf's Buzzard will be available here at the helipad whenever you need it.
MAIN.translated: 你随时可以在停机坪找到Yusuf的秃鹰直升机。

MAIN.original: Yusuf's NOOSE Tank will be available here at the Building Site whenever you need it.
MAIN.translated: 你随时可以在建筑工地找到Yusuf的NOOSE坦克。

MAIN.original: Yusuf's Super Drop Diamond will be available here at his apartment whenever you need it.
MAIN.translated: 你随时可以在Yusuf的公寓门口找到他的Super Drop Diamond。

MAIN.original: You have arranged to hang out with your friends. Meet them by going towards the ~BLIP_105~ on the radar.
MAIN.translated: 你已和朋友安排了活动。去小地图上的~BLIP_105~接他们。

MAIN.original: You have arranged to hang out with your friends. Meet them by going towards the ~BLIP_98~ on the radar.
MAIN.translated: 你已和朋友安排了活动。去小地图上的~BLIP_98~接他们。

MAIN.original: You can cancel an activity after it has been arranged. Use the option on the phone under your friend's name. They will prefer to be warned than stood up.
MAIN.translated: 在安排活动后你仍然可以取消它。使用手机中对应朋友下的选项取消。比起被放鸽子，他们更乐意事先得到通知。

MAIN.original: You can take Armando and Henrique to the location of any activity marked on the radar. As you drive other nearby activities will appear on the radar.
MAIN.translated: 你可以带Armando和Henrique去小地图上标记的任何地点。驾驶途中，小地图上还会显示附近的其它活动地点。

MAIN.original: You have completed an activity with Armando and Henrique. You can drop them off or go on another activity. You can take them on up to 4 activities.
MAIN.translated: 你已与Armando和Henrique完成了一项活动。送他们回家或再进行一项其他活动。一次约会最多进行四项活动。

MAIN.original: Armando and Henrique are ready to be dropped off now.
You are drunk. Your vision is blurred and you will find it difficult to walk and drive. Try to keep your balance. You'll sober up soon.
MAIN.translated: 你喝醉了。视线一片模糊，行走和驾驶也变得十分困难。尽量保持平衡。很快就会恢复正常的。

MAIN.original: Stop near Armando and Henrique or toot the horn to attract their attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Armando和Henrique附近，或鸣笛引起他们的注意。

MAIN.original: Stop near Armando and Henrique or toot the horn to attract their attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Armando和Henrique附近，或鸣笛引起他们的注意。

MAIN.original: Land close to Armando and Henrique to attract their attention.
MAIN.translated: 降落到Armando和Henrique附近，引起他们的注意。

MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

For The Man Who Has Everything
THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!
MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

MAIN.original: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!
MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Shit. I ain't actually sure about that. I'll have to call you back.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~妈的，我也不太清楚。待会儿再联系你。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Damn, you know what, I don't know. I'll hit you back in a minute.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~妈的，太难了，我不知道。过会儿我再打给你。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Dios. You'd think I'd know this shit. I'm gonna have to call you later.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~操，我还真不知道在哪儿。待会儿打给你。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hello, this is the LCPD, where would you like us to send an officer?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，这里是LCPD，请问您想让我们向哪里出警？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hello, you're through to the MS Paramedics. In which area is your medical emergency?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，您呼叫的是医疗服务中心，您需要在哪里的医疗应急？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hello, this is the FDLC. Where do you need assistance?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，这里是FDLC，您需要在哪里的帮助？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hello, you're through to the Liberty City Emergency Services.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~您好，您呼叫的是自由城应急服务。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Please use your touchtone keypad to select which specific service you require.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请使用您的拨号按键选择您需要的特定服务。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Press 1 for Police, press 2 for Paramedics, press 3 for the Fire Department.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~报警请按1，急救请按2，消防请按3。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~An LCPD peacekeeper will be there as soon as possible, sir.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~很快将有一名LCPD干员到达，先生。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We'll send a basically trained paramedic as soon as we can, sir.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我们会尽快派出一支训练有素的医疗小组，先生。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Don't move and please have your insurance documentation or credit card ready.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请不要离开，并准备好您的保险单证或信用卡。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We'll get a fire truck out to you right away.
~z~~x~Hold tight and please be advised that the FDLC takes no responsibility for damage to property.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~请坚持住。注意，FDLC不对过程中造成的财产损失负任何责任。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We look forward to hearing from you again. Please stay safe in the meantime.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我们期待您的下次来电。同时请您注意安全。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I'm sorry, but all our peacekeepers are currently busy filling quotas and dealing with paper work.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~很抱歉，但目前我们的干员都忙于完成指标以及书面工作。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~All our lines are busy at the moment, please call again later. Your emergency is important to us.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~目前我们的电话全部占线，请稍后再拨。您的紧急状况对我们十分重要。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Oye, there's something to be said for this place.
~z~~x~I should be working one of these clubs.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这家店才是我该工作的地方。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This place is actually a lot more honest than where I work.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这里可比我工作的地方实诚多了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Damn mami, we could have some fun later on.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~妈的，姑娘，待会儿我们找点乐子吧。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Diablo, girl. You way too fine to be working here.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~妈的，姑娘。你在这儿上班可惜了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You should come to work for me, mami.
~z~~x~I could watch that ass all day.
~z~~x~Ay Dios mio, the things I would do to you...
~z~~x~I knew it would take two of you to handle me.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我就知道你们要两个人才能服侍我。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Oye, you girls are gonna have to fight over me later.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~喂，你们待会儿再为了我吵架吧。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Where's the third one? Two ain't enough.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~没第三个了吗？两个还不太够。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This cold, mami. You ain't even giving up your number.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~太糟了，姑娘。你都不肯给我电话号码。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Thank you, baby. I think I'm gonna have to sit down for a minute.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~谢谢你，宝贝。我还想再坐一会儿。
